  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Erik Bane used to be Proctor-General of the Necromunda Enforcers; now disgrace, addiction and the Underhive have ground him almost flat. When a girl flees into his settlement with the Razorheads behind her, Bane's old instincts drag him back into danger just as the Neurone Plague turns the tunnels into a near-zombie outbreak. He gathers survivors, fights gangers and Redemptionist zealots, and tries to stay useful long enough to matter again. Grim Necromunda survival horror, with a fallen lawman at its tired heart.",
